{"tid":6032,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人知咩叫蒙提霍爾理論？🤓","createTime":"2016-11-27T06:59:23.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-04T04:07:08.000Z","uid":19794,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d108d810c64f74f1f921d03ea3d8e96e1b897008","tid":6032,"uid":19794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T06:59:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kIo0EpetyEw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DkIo0EpetyEw&d=9qwVmVD3aCsyYotQX9g%2BG8W%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=f82dad5b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kIo0EpetyEw</a><br />\n<br />\n佢解釋得好奇怪<br />\n<br />\n首先，主持人開了一道門之後，選擇就得兩個二選一。所以主持人開左門之後係咪應該得50%？<br />\n<br />\n跟住，如果not swapping 獲得汽車既機會是係33%<br />\n但係如果swapping <br />\n你就必須先選中山羊（33%) 然後才能獲得汽車（66%或者50%）<br />\n那機會率唔係應該33%x66%（或者50%）＝21%咩？<br />\n其實應該仲少先係？<br />\n<br />\n有無人話比我聽我咁諗岩唔岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：dse數學F"},{"pid":"2cae0e6dedab927bcb67ceaa49aff3995d9b74a8","tid":6032,"uid":19794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T07:03:02.000Z","msg":"有無人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6b948295779dcfc9c51a8e6f52367f4edc388b5","tid":6032,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T07:11:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你就必須先選中山羊（33%) 然後才能獲得汽車（66%或者50%）<br />\n那機會率唔係應該33%x66%（或者50%）＝21%咩？<br />\n其實應該仲少先係？</blockquote><br />\n一開波選中山羊係66%<br />\n<br />\n如果你not swapping 咁你就要一開波揀中架車<br />\n姐係33%中到架車<br />\n<br />\n如果你swapping 咁你一開波只要揀中山羊(66%)<br />\n因為個主持會開一道門 而果道門一定係山羊<br />\n只要你swapping 就一定揀中架車<br />\n所以一開波揀山羊再轉 就會贏到車"},{"pid":"7390c7d3f6cba84026652e3d9fd65a96c1772ecc","tid":6032,"uid":15164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T07:14:13.000Z","msg":"係咪因為2個係indepenent case <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1f16d67b70ab2ec69e2a9d52e869bec2faa20a3","tid":6032,"uid":15164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T07:15:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪因為2個係<span style=\"color: red;\">independent</span> case <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"d60dcc740d4fb7756ef9422d815f5b7d0ebc8a0b","tid":6032,"uid":29397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T07:20:11.000Z","msg":"你聆聽同閱讀理解都係F <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84ee0ec0d1f2b2d5a3c80406e302153c8dac42f9","tid":6032,"uid":26215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T07:30:10.000Z","msg":"即係你一開始揀中山羊既機率一定大D 中左山羊之後<br />\n佢開多道山羊 咁另一道就一定係車   但係一開始中車就冇得講 <br />\n 咁我梗係駁一開始有66%中羊 再換<br />\n<br />\n係咪咁 錯左唔好屌咁大力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50cb1074e1c0a1360e57345f34dabd91210ccd20","tid":6032,"uid":18739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T07:34:59.000Z","msg":"依個問題係以前高登引起勁多討論😂<br />\n我最喜歡一個答案，<br />\n<br />\n你幻想下唔係3對門，<br />\n可能係1000對門，<br />\n你揀左1對門之後，<br />\n<br />\n主持人會關哂其他無獎品的門，<br />\n得返2揀1，<br />\n<br />\n咁調轉黎諗，<br />\n你一開始要揀中有獎品的門的機率係1000分之一，正常人梗係轉啦，你邊會咁好彩一開始就揀中有獎品的門呀。"},{"pid":"02d6debcc0b0aff60fc16ed7d1771c92bb04d63c","tid":6032,"uid":19794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T09:07:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你聆聽同閱讀理解都係F <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌 Sor 係我打錯左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d46a084203ae125c0a094ee32ac79700be66029d","tid":6032,"uid":24639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T10:35:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>依個問題係以前高登引起勁多討論😂<br />\n我最喜歡一個答案，<br />\n<br />\n你幻想下唔係3對門，<br />\n可能係1000對門，<br />\n你揀左1對門